    "Data Overview, Visualization Analyisis and PreprocessingThe first dataset used for sentiment analysis is the Amazon customer review dataset provided by Amazon S3, containing 130 million customers available for academic research, and comprising of 46 subsets corresponding to each category, in addition to multilingual subsets from outside the US.",
